Last week ⭐️
1. Spilled coffee on my new tshirt 
2. Made breakfast every single day
3. Got ready to go out but took a nap instead
4. Holi party for 2
5. Love dal k paranthe 
6. Just a beautiful flower shop, took this from cab
7. Late night cravings: peanut butter garlic noodles
8. Not enough space for my ceramics 
9. Made a tinnie tiny clay art ice cream
9. Snack on the go
10. Made decent latte art after a long time
11. Beautiful spring flowers everywhere
12. Lover got a new haircut
